title: FurReal friends FRR WALKALOTS Big Wags Dog 2.0
description: Pet Walkers Wanted! What'S More Fun Than Walking A Pet? Walking Lots Of Them! Furreal Walkalots Pets Feature A Connectable System That Lets Kids Walk One Pet, Or Their Favourite Pack! This Pet Comes With A Two-Part Detachable Leash To Walk Him Across The Floor As Well As A Connector To Add Up To Two Walkalots Lil’ Wags Pets (Sold Separately). Push Him Along By His Leash And He’Ll Move Forward With His Wobbling Head, Signature Bouncy Walk, And Spring-Activated Tail Motion. He Also Makes Sounds And Funny Noises, Making The Walk Feel That Much More Real. Shall We Take A Stroll Around The House? Sounds Like Fun!Cuddly Pet You Can Take For A Walk. Connectable System Lets You Walk One Pet Or Walk A Lot. Features Sounds, Funny Noises, Bouncy Walk, And Tail Motion. Includes Pet, Leash (2 Pieces), Handle, Connector, And Instructions.
